{"storyMeta":{"storyReviewType":"NONE","storyId":"act35side_level_act35side_06_beg","storyGroup":"act35side","storySort":13,"storyDependence":"act35side_level_act35side_st02","storyCanShow":1,"storyCode":"AS-6","storyName":"过往云烟","storyPic":null,"storyInfo":"祖拜尔使用源石技艺唤醒无数的构装体，要将整座城市恢复为之前的宝库，所有人危在旦夕。然后，祖拜尔委托两位兽主为娜仁图亚和佩佩分别设下考验。","storyCanEnter":1,"storyTxt":"activities/act35side/level_act35side_06_beg","avgTag":"行动前","unLockType":"STAGE_CLEAR","costItemType":"NONE","costItemId":null,"costItemCount":0,"stageCount":1,"requiredStages":[{"stageId":"act35side_06","minState":"PLAYED","maxState":"COMPLETE"}],"prev":11,"next":13,"characters":["？？？","佩佩","梅捷缇克缇","电台广播","祖拜尔","拉恕尔","米奥","沃奥"]},"lines":[{"type":"header","key":"title_test","skippable":"true","mode":"BLACK_MASK","id":0},{"type":"stopmusic","id":1},{"type":"dialog","id":2},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":3},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":4},{"type":"charslot","id":5},{"type":"background","image":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/d9/Avg_bg_53_g8_sargondeluxeroom.png","screenadapt":"coverall","id":6},{"type":"playmusic","intro":"$darkness01_intro","key":"https://static.prts.wiki/music/music/beta1_180603/m_dia_darkness01_loop.mp3","volume":"0.6","id":7,"musicid":0},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_summercicada","volume":"1","loop":"true","channel":"s","id":8},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":9},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":10},{"type":"text","text":"室内，空气因为酷暑而变得沉闷，女孩坐在桌前，一边翻着厚厚的资料，一边擦拭从额角流下的汗水。","id":11},{"type":"text","text":"背后响起了脚步声，她知道有人进来了，但却懒得回头看。","id":12},{"type":"text","text":"桌子上有扁桃仁，他会自己拿的。","id":13},{"type":"dialog","id":14},{"type":"soundvolume","volume":"0.1","channel":"s","fadetime":"2","id":15},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4058_pepe_1#2$1","posfrom":"0,-20","posto":"0,-20","duration":"1.5","isblock":"true","id":16},{"type":"delay","time":"0.5","id":17},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","focus":"n","id":18},{"type":"dialogue","name":"？？？","text":"姐姐，你在看什么书啊？","id":19},{"type":"dialog","id":20},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4058_pepe_1#2$1","id":21},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_paper1","volume":"1","id":22},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":23},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4058_pepe_1#2$1","id":24},{"type":"dialogue","name":"佩佩","text":"......","id":25,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/56/Avg_avg_4058_pepe_1-2$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","focus":"n","id":26},{"type":"dialogue","name":"？？？","text":"姐姐，下午太阳这么好，出去玩啊！","id":27},{"type":"dialog","id":28},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4058_pepe_1#2$1","id":29},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_paper2","volume":"1","id":30},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":31},{"type":"dialogue","name":"佩佩","text":"......","id":32,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/56/Avg_avg_4058_pepe_1-2$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","focus":"n","id":33},{"type":"dialogue","name":"？？？","text":"姐姐，你不会打算钻在这堆落灰的莎草纸卷里一辈子吧？","id":34},{"type":"dialog","id":35},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4058_pepe_1#8$1","id":36},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_paper1","volume":"1","id":37},{"type":"delay","time":"0.5","id":38},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_paper2","volume":"1","id":39},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":40},{"type":"dialogue","name":"佩佩","text":"......","id":41,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/6/69/Avg_avg_4058_pepe_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","focus":"n","id":42},{"type":"dialogue","name":"？？？","text":"姐姐，我去请求父亲了，他说他会考虑让我成为黄金之城的史官。","id":43},{"type":"dialog","id":44},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_paper1","volume":"1","id":45},{"type":"delay","time":"0.5","id":46},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_paper2","volume":"1","id":47},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":48},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4058_pepe_1#8$1","id":49},{"type":"dialogue","name":"佩佩","text":"......","id":50,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/6/69/Avg_avg_4058_pepe_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","focus":"n","id":51},{"type":"dialogue","name":"？？？","text":"姐姐，做个帕夏也很好，放弃吧。","id":52},{"type":"dialog","id":53},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4058_pepe_1#9$2","posfrom":"0,-20","posto":"0,0","afrom":"1","ato":"1","duration":"0.3","isblock":"true","id":54},{"type":"dialogue","name":"佩佩","text":"够了！你小子别吵我了！","id":55,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/a/ab/Avg_avg_4058_pepe_1-9$2.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":56},{"type":"musicvolume","volume":"0","fadetime":"1","id":57},{"type":"stopsound","channel":"s","fadetime":"1","id":58},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_clothmovement","volume":"1","id":59},{"type":"charslot","duration":"0.2","isblock":"true","id":60},{"type":"camerashake","duration":"0.3","xstrength":"30","ystrength":"30","vibrato":"30","randomness":"90","fadeout":"true","block":"false","id":61},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_bookdrop","volume":"1","id":62},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":63},{"type":"text","text":"女孩猛地回过头，却发现背后空无一人。","id":64},{"type":"text","text":"只有她掷出的书卷，孤零零地躺在地板上。","id":65},{"type":"dialog","id":66},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4058_pepe_1#8$2","id":67},{"type":"delay","time":"1.5","id":68},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4058_pepe_1#5$1","duration":"1","isblock":"true","id":69},{"type":"delay","time":"1.5","id":70},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","focus":"n","id":71},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_knockdoorfast","volume":"1","id":72},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":73},{"type":"dialogue","name":"梅捷缇克缇","text":"佩佩，你在吗？快开门！","id":74},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4058_pepe_1#12$1","id":75},{"type":"dialogue","name":"佩佩","text":"我在，请进。","id":76,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/c/c7/Avg_avg_4058_pepe_1-12$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":77},{"type":"charslot","id":78},{"type":"playsound","key":"$dooropenquite","volume":"1","id":79},{"type":"delay","time":"1.5","id":80},{"type":"musicvolume","volume":"0.6","fadetime":"2","id":81},{"type":"playsound","key":"$rungeneral","volume":"1","id":82},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_4058_pepe_1#12$1","id":83},{"type":"delay","time":"0.5","id":84},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_1478_1#1$1","posfrom":"200,0","posto":"0,0","duration":"0.5","isblock":"true","id":85},{"type":"delay","time":"0.5","id":86},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_1478_1#7$1","focus":"r","id":87},{"type":"dialogue","name":"梅捷缇克缇","text":"我给你的通讯器发了那么多消息，你为什么不回？","id":88,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/48/Avg_avg_npc_1478_1-7$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_4058_pepe_1#12$1","focus":"l","id":89},{"type":"dialogue","name":"佩佩","text":"我把通讯器关掉，在这里看了一晚上的书，发生什么了？","id":90,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/c/c7/Avg_avg_4058_pepe_1-12$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_1478_1#6$1","focus":"r","id":91},{"type":"dialogue","name":"梅捷缇克缇","text":"哈，昨夜发生那么多事情，难不成你在这里一无所知吗？","id":92,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/1/12/Avg_avg_npc_1478_1-6$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_4058_pepe_1#12$1","focus":"l","id":93},{"type":"dialogue","name":"佩佩","text":"我不知道啊。","id":94,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/c/c7/Avg_avg_4058_pepe_1-12$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_1478_1#6$1","focus":"r","id":95},{"type":"multiline","name":"梅捷缇克缇","text":"你这个闷起头来做事的性子真的是......","id":96},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_1478_1#2$1","focus":"r","id":97},{"type":"multiline","name":"梅捷缇克缇","end":"true","text":"算了，我也不知道该说什么了。","id":98},{"type":"dialog","id":99},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_button","volume":"1","id":100},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":101},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_1478_1#1$1","focus":"r","id":102},{"type":"dialogue","name":"梅捷缇克缇","text":"直接听吧。","id":103,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/9/96/Avg_avg_npc_1478_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":104},{"type":"charslot","id":105},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_oldtvelectricity","volume":"0","loop":"true","channel":"o","id":106},{"type":"soundvolume","volume":"1","channel":"o","fadetime":"2","id":107},{"type":"dialogue","name":"电台广播","text":"米城内多个区域发生紧急事件。","id":108},{"type":"dialogue","name":"电台广播","text":"有大量金属构装的人偶走上街头，从居民家中抢夺大量宝石后离开。","id":109},{"type":"dialogue","name":"电台广播","text":"据悉，已有众多市民向城市护卫队报告，护卫队队长表示正在追查中。","id":110},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4058_pepe_1#8$1","id":111},{"type":"dialogue","name":"佩佩","text":"金属人偶......？","id":112,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/6/69/Avg_avg_4058_pepe_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","id":113},{"type":"dialogue","name":"电台广播","text":"据目击者透露，他曾于昨夜目睹这些金属构装人偶从本市博物馆中逃出......","id":114},{"type":"dialog","id":115},{"type":"stopsound","channel":"o","fadetime":"2","id":116},{"type":"camerashake","duration":"0.3","xstrength":"30","ystrength":"30","vibrato":"30","randomness":"90","fadeout":"true","block":"false","id":117},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_1478_1#1$1","focus":"n","id":118},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_4058_pepe_1#9$1","focus":"l","id":119},{"type":"dialogue","name":"佩佩","text":"什么？！","id":120,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/8/8f/Avg_avg_4058_pepe_1-9$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_1478_1#1$1","focus":"r","id":121},{"type":"dialogue","name":"梅捷缇克缇","text":"那个......我想说的，她都说了。","id":122,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/9/96/Avg_avg_npc_1478_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"梅捷缇克缇","text":"阿娜特说，博物馆的工作人员跟随着构装体的踪迹，最后找到了大巴扎。","id":123,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/9/96/Avg_avg_npc_1478_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_4058_pepe_1#8$1","focus":"l","id":124},{"type":"dialogue","name":"佩佩","text":"是祖拜尔做的吗？","id":125,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/6/69/Avg_avg_4058_pepe_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_1478_1#1$1","focus":"r","id":126},{"type":"dialogue","name":"梅捷缇克缇","text":"我们怀疑是这样，但是没人看到他，你和他相处时间最久，你能去找找看吗？","id":127,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/9/96/Avg_avg_npc_1478_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_4058_pepe_1#8$1","focus":"l","id":128},{"type":"dialogue","name":"佩佩","text":"知道了，我这就过去。","id":129,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/6/69/Avg_avg_4058_pepe_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"佩佩","text":"那你和阿娜特呢？","id":130,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/6/69/Avg_avg_4058_pepe_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_1478_1#1$1","focus":"r","id":131},{"type":"dialogue","name":"梅捷缇克缇","text":"作为博物馆的管理人员，我们总得将文物尽数找回来。","id":132,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/9/96/Avg_avg_npc_1478_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"梅捷缇克缇","text":"我们打算去街上看看。","id":133,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/9/96/Avg_avg_npc_1478_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_4058_pepe_1#8$1","focus":"l","id":134},{"type":"dialogue","name":"佩佩","text":"一有消息我就通知你们，回见。","id":135,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/6/69/Avg_avg_4058_pepe_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":136},{"type":"playsound","key":"$rungeneral","volume":"1","id":137},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","posfrom":"0,0","posto":"-200,0","afrom":"1","ato":"0","duration":"0.5","isblock":"true","id":138},{"type":"delay","time":"1.5","id":139},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_1478_1#2$1","id":140},{"type":"dialogue","name":"梅捷缇克缇","text":"呼......","id":141,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/6/63/Avg_avg_npc_1478_1-2$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":142},{"type":"charslot","id":143},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_oldtvelectricity","volume":"0","loop":"true","channel":"o","id":144},{"type":"soundvolume","volume":"1","channel":"o","fadetime":"2","id":145},{"type":"dialogue","name":"电台广播","text":"呃，慢着，本台插播一条急讯。","id":146},{"type":"dialogue","name":"电台广播","text":"有市民发现家中取水器内流出的水变得浑浊，其中掺杂大量泥沙。","id":147},{"type":"dialogue","name":"电台广播","text":"护卫队方面称，他们正在紧急组织人力排查城市老地下水通道，由于通道情况复杂，可能仍然需要时间......","id":148},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1478_1#5$1","id":149},{"type":"dialogue","name":"梅捷缇克缇","text":"啊，这又是什么情况？","id":150,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/8/85/Avg_avg_npc_1478_1-5$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":151},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"2","id":152},{"type":"stopsound","channel":"o","fadetime":"2","id":153},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":154},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":155},{"type":"charslot","id":156},{"type":"background","image":"https://media.prts.wiki/6/62/Avg_bg_53_g10_grandbazaar_d.png","screenadapt":"coverall","id":157},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":158},{"type":"playmusic","key":"https://static.prts.wiki/music/music/avg/m_avg_memory_loop.mp3","volume":"0.6","id":159,"musicid":1},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":160},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":161},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_fsmummy","volume":"1","id":162},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1479_1#1$1","duration":"1.5","isblock":"true","id":163},{"type":"dialogue","name":"祖拜尔","text":"......某人已经给我讲述过这里的故事。","id":164,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/7/72/Avg_avg_npc_1479_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"祖拜尔","text":"宝石繁荣了大巴扎，与香料、绸缎、工艺品一同源源不断地为这里带来财富。","id":165,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/7/72/Avg_avg_npc_1479_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"祖拜尔","text":"借由宝石交易所，借由这些有着特殊源石回路的宝石，米纳特哈玛仪成为镶嵌在沙海中的一颗晨星......","id":166,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/7/72/Avg_avg_npc_1479_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":167},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_bellshake","volume":"1","id":168},{"type":"charslot","duration":"1.5","isblock":"true","id":169},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_sandstone","volume":"1","id":170},{"type":"effect","name":"$e_sandfall_01","layer":"1","id":171},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_sand_lp","volume":"0","loop":"true","channel":"sa","id":172},{"type":"soundvolume","volume":"1","channel":"sa","fadetime":"2","id":173},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":174},{"type":"text","text":"古老的建筑不断淌下黄沙，人们推开窗户或走出大门，惊异地看向自己祖祖辈辈生活的房屋，继而看向站在街道中央的祖拜尔。","id":175},{"type":"text","text":"但祖拜尔却仿佛没有注意到他们。","id":176},{"type":"stopsound","channel":"sa","fadetime":"2","id":177},{"type":"text","text":"他俯身从黄沙中拾起一枚首饰，螺旋形金属框架正中的宝石在日光下熠熠生辉。","id":178},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4140_lasher_1#1$1","id":179},{"type":"dialogue","name":"拉恕尔","text":"祖拜尔先生，您提起的壁画就在前方。","id":180,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/1/18/Avg_avg_4140_lasher_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"拉恕尔","text":"我的外祖父曾说过，墙上的图画描绘了古萨尔贡人的生活，记录着米纳特哈玛仪的诞生。","id":181,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/1/18/Avg_avg_4140_lasher_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4140_lasher_1#3$1","id":182},{"type":"dialogue","name":"拉恕尔","text":"“即便河水干涸，城市被掩埋在黄沙之下，它也不会褪色。”","id":183,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/8/8f/Avg_avg_4140_lasher_1-3$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1479_1#3$1","id":184},{"type":"dialogue","name":"祖拜尔","text":"......“不会褪色”，是的。就如同你我手中流过的每一颗宝石。","id":185,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/37/Avg_avg_npc_1479_1-3$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"祖拜尔","text":"只不过，不是河水干涸，黄沙掩埋了昔日的城市。","id":186,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/37/Avg_avg_npc_1479_1-3$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"祖拜尔","text":"而是洪水毁去了那伟大建筑的顶端，黄沙深处掩埋的辉煌成了千年的秘密。","id":187,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/37/Avg_avg_npc_1479_1-3$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":188},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":189},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":190},{"type":"charslot","id":191},{"type":"cgitem","image":"cgitem_53_i04_1","style":"cg","pfrom":"-585,0","pto":"-730,0","pduration":"20","sfrom":"1","sto":"1.35","sduration":"25","layer":"1","id":192},{"type":"cgitem","image":"cgitem_53_i04_2","style":"cg","pfrom":"0,-233","pto":"20,-330","pduration":"20","sfrom":"1","sto":"1.35","sduration":"25","layer":"2","id":193},{"type":"cgitem","image":"cgitem_53_i04_3","style":"cg","pfrom":"-230,0","pto":"-270,0","pduration":"30","sfrom":"1","sto":"1.15","sduration":"30","layer":"3","id":194},{"type":"image","image":"https://media.prts.wiki/6/64/Avg_53_i04.png","screenadapt":"coverall","id":195},{"type":"imagetween","xScaleFrom":"1","yScaleFrom":"1","xScaleTo":"1.06","yScaleTo":"1.06","ease":"OutQuad","duration":"30","block":"false","id":196},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":197},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":198},{"type":"dialogue","name":"祖拜尔","text":"每一次日升月落，都是一个小轮回的重新演绎。","id":199},{"type":"dialogue","name":"祖拜尔","text":"短暂的一天是如此，漫长的一生是如此......","id":200},{"type":"dialogue","name":"祖拜尔","text":"城市的枯荣，帝国的盛衰，大地的终始，亦是如此。","id":201},{"type":"dialogue","name":"拉恕尔","text":"我想，虽然壁画只能记载下万古之中的一瞬，但这一瞬同样会一遍遍轮回重演，这就是它的价值。","id":202},{"type":"dialogue","name":"祖拜尔","text":"沙阿命人绘制这些壁画，并不是为了自己的名在轮回中留存。","id":203},{"type":"dialogue","name":"祖拜尔","text":"他要留下的是他对时间与生命的解释本身，在那之后，世人便有可以效仿的依据。","id":204},{"type":"dialogue","name":"祖拜尔","text":"“过去与未来之王”在此地建设了他的宝库，于是他身后漫长的“阿斯兰战争”里，无数王酋觊觎此地。","id":205},{"type":"dialogue","name":"祖拜尔","text":"直到极南的热风让气候发生巨变，这里迎来滔天洪水，城墙倾颓，河流改道，土地变得面目全非。","id":206},{"type":"dialogue","name":"祖拜尔","text":"人们在黄沙中搜寻宝库的痕迹，却一无所获，于是他们开始相信，宝库已经随着洪水覆灭。","id":207},{"type":"dialogue","name":"祖拜尔","text":"王酋的寻宝队离开了，工匠和商人们来到这里，在河边建起了新的聚落。","id":208},{"type":"dialogue","name":"祖拜尔","text":"我始终看着这一切。","id":209},{"type":"dialogue","name":"祖拜尔","text":"我奉命守护这座宝库，这是我的职责。","id":210},{"type":"dialogue","name":"祖拜尔","text":"我徘徊在黄沙之中，历尽日升日落，拦阻那些窥探秘密的不轨之徒。","id":211},{"type":"dialogue","name":"祖拜尔","text":"而你，年轻人，你应该比任何人都更加确定——沙阿宝库的本体，就在这座城市的地底。","id":212},{"type":"dialog","id":213},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":214},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"3","block":"true","id":215},{"type":"image","id":216},{"type":"hidecgitem","image":"cgitem_53_i04_1","id":217},{"type":"hidecgitem","image":"cgitem_53_i04_2","id":218},{"type":"hidecgitem","image":"cgitem_53_i04_3","id":219},{"type":"background","image":"https://media.prts.wiki/6/62/Avg_bg_53_g10_grandbazaar_d.png","screenadapt":"coverall","id":220},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":221},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1479_1#3$1","id":222},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":223},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":224},{"type":"dialogue","name":"祖拜尔","text":"“第四颗代表肝脏，我们清醒着进入夜晚，为了职责与义务。”......感谢你归还的宝石，让我回忆起更多往事。","id":225,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/37/Avg_avg_npc_1479_1-3$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"祖拜尔","text":"最初，成千上万的能工巧匠来到一片荒芜的米纳特哈玛仪。","id":226,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/37/Avg_avg_npc_1479_1-3$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"祖拜尔","text":"上至奇伟的黄金机关迷宫，下至手工雕琢的源石回路宝石，工匠们创造了一切，然后将它们埋入黄沙。","id":227,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/37/Avg_avg_npc_1479_1-3$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"祖拜尔","text":"后世的人们大都相信，在耗尽心血的作业之后，所有的工匠也都被埋葬在了他们的造物身边。","id":228,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/37/Avg_avg_npc_1479_1-3$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"祖拜尔","text":"但实际上，仍有一些工匠隐居在米纳特哈玛仪西南的一处村落，世代保守着“宝库入口在何地”的秘密。","id":229,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/37/Avg_avg_npc_1479_1-3$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4140_lasher_1#2$1","id":230},{"type":"dialogue","name":"拉恕尔","text":"......","id":231,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/f/f2/Avg_avg_4140_lasher_1-2$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1479_1#2$1","id":232},{"type":"dialogue","name":"祖拜尔","text":"该你来说了，年轻人。","id":233,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/0/0b/Avg_avg_npc_1479_1-2$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"祖拜尔","text":"接下来的事情，便与你的家族有关了。","id":234,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/0/0b/Avg_avg_npc_1479_1-2$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","id":235},{"type":"text","text":"年轻的监管人紧闭双目，似乎被沉重的记忆之沙淹没。","id":236},{"type":"text","text":"那段故事经过世代流传，已经成为高悬于思绪荒漠上空的烈日，仰首便可望见。","id":237},{"type":"text","text":"蒸腾着。炙烤着。煎熬着。","id":238},{"type":"dialog","id":239},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4140_lasher_1#2$1","duration":"1","isblock":"true","id":240},{"type":"dialogue","name":"拉恕尔","text":"......三百年前，许多帕夏王酋集结的军队找到了那个村子。","id":241,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/f/f2/Avg_avg_4140_lasher_1-2$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"拉恕尔","text":"他们向村民们逼问宝库的入口，坚持守密的人都被砍去了双手。","id":242,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/f/f2/Avg_avg_4140_lasher_1-2$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"拉恕尔","text":"因为不忍村民们继续受害，一位失去双手的宝石工匠主动找上王酋军，提出要为他们引路。","id":243,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/f/f2/Avg_avg_4140_lasher_1-2$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"拉恕尔","text":"在宝库前，他见证了王酋军与宝库守护者的激战，看到守护者虽然被打败，但没有他的法术，宝库的大门便不会开启。","id":244,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/f/f2/Avg_avg_4140_lasher_1-2$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"拉恕尔","text":"愤怒的王酋军剖开了守护者的胸膛，刮下了他身体内外镶嵌的每一颗宝石。","id":245,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/f/f2/Avg_avg_4140_lasher_1-2$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"拉恕尔","text":"尽管那位告密的工匠用尽所知的技术，指导自己年幼的孩子去修复守护者的身躯，但守护者终究没有醒来。","id":246,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/f/f2/Avg_avg_4140_lasher_1-2$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"拉恕尔","text":"......然后，米纳特哈玛仪的大巴扎立起了一架天平。那个工匠的孩子在成人之后安葬了守护者，又设立了一间宝石交易所。","id":247,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/f/f2/Avg_avg_4140_lasher_1-2$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"拉恕尔","text":"从那以后，他的后人一直在这里等待。","id":248,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/f/f2/Avg_avg_4140_lasher_1-2$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"拉恕尔","text":"每一代先祖都竭尽所能，让米纳特哈玛仪的宝石贸易更加繁荣。","id":249,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/f/f2/Avg_avg_4140_lasher_1-2$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"拉恕尔","text":"百年千年，终有一日，人们能淘尽萨尔贡的黄沙，宝石会聚在这座城市......","id":250,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/f/f2/Avg_avg_4140_lasher_1-2$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"拉恕尔","text":"......我能够将它们还给您。","id":251,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/f/f2/Avg_avg_4140_lasher_1-2$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":252},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_bellshake","volume":"1","id":253},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":254},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":255},{"type":"text","text":"感觉到叉铃抵上胸膛，监管人不敢睁开双眼。","id":256},{"type":"text","text":"但在他的眼前，却仿佛有数百年的时光在瞬间流淌而过。","id":257},{"type":"text","text":"日升月落，物换星移。监管人看到一座座城市兴荣，复又消亡，眼前的建筑缓慢地化为沙砾。","id":258},{"type":"dialog","id":259},{"type":"charslot","id":260},{"type":"background","id":261},{"type":"image","image":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/40/Avg_53_i09_1.png","screenadapt":"coverall","id":262},{"type":"bgeffect","name":"$eb_ancestor","layer":"1","id":263},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":264},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"3","block":"true","id":265},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":266},{"type":"text","text":"监管人看到一位古老的守护者行走在无边际的沙漠中。","id":267},{"type":"text","text":"守护者张开双臂，沐浴在繁星的光芒之下，面向东方等待着日出。","id":268},{"type":"text","text":"感知到有人在看自己，他垂下视线迎向监管人的目光。","id":269},{"type":"dialog","id":270},{"type":"image","image":"https://media.prts.wiki/2/25/Avg_53_i09_2.png","screenadapt":"coverall","fadetime":"1.5","id":271},{"type":"delay","time":"1.5","id":272},{"type":"text","text":"在守护者悲悯的注视中，监管人不禁颤抖。","id":273},{"type":"text","text":"为他即将吐露的话语。","id":274},{"type":"dialogue","name":"祖拜尔","text":"......多么漫长的时光啊。","id":275},{"type":"dialogue","name":"祖拜尔","text":"你们自由了。","id":276},{"type":"dialog","id":277},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"3","id":278},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":279},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"3","block":"true","id":280},{"type":"image","id":281},{"type":"bgeffect","id":282},{"type":"charslot","id":283},{"type":"background","image":"https://media.prts.wiki/c/c6/Avg_bg_53_g12_gemexchange.png","screenadapt":"coverall","id":284},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":285},{"type":"playmusic","key":"https://static.prts.wiki/music/music/act28side/m_avg_wasteland_loop.mp3","volume":"0.6","id":286,"musicid":2},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":287},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_fsmummy","volume":"1","id":288},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1479_1#1$1","duration":"1.5","isblock":"true","id":289},{"type":"dialogue","name":"祖拜尔","text":"好久不见了，二位。","id":290,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/7/72/Avg_avg_npc_1479_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1479_1#2$1","id":291},{"type":"dialogue","name":"祖拜尔","text":"过去数百年，我有失于自己的职责，但如今我已重返人世，我将同这座城市一起，赎还我们欠下的时光。","id":292,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/0/0b/Avg_avg_npc_1479_1-2$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1482_1#1$1","id":293},{"type":"dialogue","name":"米奥","text":"......","id":294,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/d5/Avg_avg_npc_1482_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1479_1#4$1","id":295},{"type":"dialogue","name":"祖拜尔","text":"与此同时，我还有一个请求，希望二位能够答应。","id":296,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/6/6b/Avg_avg_npc_1479_1-4$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"祖拜尔","text":"如果那位梦魇当真是哈兰杜汗的后裔，我将应沙阿之诺，为她打开宝库。","id":297,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/6/6b/Avg_avg_npc_1479_1-4$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1479_1#1$1","id":298},{"type":"dialogue","name":"祖拜尔","text":"沃奥，请确认她的血脉。","id":299,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/7/72/Avg_avg_npc_1479_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":300},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_dogbarknormal","volume":"1","id":301},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1483_1#1$1","id":302},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":303},{"type":"dialogue","name":"沃奥","text":"交由我便是。","id":304,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/c/c5/Avg_avg_npc_1483_1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1479_1#1$1","id":305},{"type":"dialogue","name":"祖拜尔","text":"以及，我仍然需要对她进行一番考验，若她最终无法走上天途，注定不算是合格的梦魇。","id":306,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/7/72/Avg_avg_npc_1479_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"祖拜尔","text":"无论如何，让她踏出那一步。","id":307,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/7/72/Avg_avg_npc_1479_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1483_1#1$1","id":308},{"type":"dialogue","name":"沃奥","text":"我明白。","id":309,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/c/c5/Avg_avg_npc_1483_1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1482_1#4$1","id":310},{"type":"dialogue","name":"米奥","text":"我不会也要一起去吧？我对那些梦魇可没有什么好感。","id":311,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/58/Avg_avg_npc_1482_1-4$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"米奥","text":"他们中的酒鬼含量实在是太高了，把酒液洒得到处都是，我可不想费心再去舔自己的皮毛。","id":312,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/58/Avg_avg_npc_1482_1-4$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1479_1#1$1","id":313},{"type":"dialogue","name":"祖拜尔","text":"不，米奥，您需要帮我完成另外一项事情。","id":314,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/7/72/Avg_avg_npc_1479_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1482_1#1$1","id":315},{"type":"dialogue","name":"米奥","text":"说吧，年轻人。","id":316,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/d5/Avg_avg_npc_1482_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1479_1#2$1","id":317},{"type":"dialogue","name":"祖拜尔","text":"在我陷入沉睡之后，沙阿的宝库遭受了如此严重的破坏，这是我的失职。","id":318,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/0/0b/Avg_avg_npc_1479_1-2$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"祖拜尔","text":"我不得不承认，即使有构装体在侧协助，我的力量也无法与王酋帕夏集结的军队相抗衡。","id":319,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/0/0b/Avg_avg_npc_1479_1-2$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1482_1#1$1","id":320},{"type":"dialogue","name":"米奥","text":"告诉我你的决定，我会为你做到，一如既往。","id":321,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/d5/Avg_avg_npc_1482_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1479_1#3$1","id":322},{"type":"dialogue","name":"祖拜尔","text":"我遇到了一个孩子，我觉得她能帮我。","id":323,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/37/Avg_avg_npc_1479_1-3$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"祖拜尔","text":"她追寻着沙阿离去的足迹，找到了我流失在外的宝石，没有她我无法苏醒。","id":324,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/37/Avg_avg_npc_1479_1-3$1.png"},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_meowlong","volume":"1","id":325},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1482_1#2$1","id":326},{"type":"dialogue","name":"米奥","text":"啊，你是说那个孩子吗？我见过她，很不错的孩子。","id":327,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/2/22/Avg_avg_npc_1482_1-2$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"米奥","text":"上进，活泼，就是有些执拗了。","id":328,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/2/22/Avg_avg_npc_1482_1-2$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"米奥","text":"让我想起了她。","id":329,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/2/22/Avg_avg_npc_1482_1-2$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1479_1#3$1","id":330},{"type":"dialogue","name":"祖拜尔","text":"是呀，当我寻回自己的记忆后，那女孩的行为举止都令我感到熟悉。","id":331,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/37/Avg_avg_npc_1479_1-3$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1479_1#2$1","id":332},{"type":"dialogue","name":"祖拜尔","text":"一如当年，我与姐姐漫步在黄金之城的街巷中，那里的一砖一瓦，她都清楚它们的来由。","id":333,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/0/0b/Avg_avg_npc_1479_1-2$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"祖拜尔","text":"对那些上了年头的东西，她总是格外着迷。","id":334,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/0/0b/Avg_avg_npc_1479_1-2$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1482_1#2$1","id":335},{"type":"dialogue","name":"米奥","text":"你需要那女孩为你做什么，祖拜尔？","id":336,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/2/22/Avg_avg_npc_1482_1-2$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1479_1#2$1","id":337},{"type":"dialogue","name":"祖拜尔","text":"我需要一个同伴，与我共同等候沙阿的归来。","id":338,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/0/0b/Avg_avg_npc_1479_1-2$1.png"},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_bellshake","volume":"1","id":339},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1479_1#1$1","id":340},{"type":"dialogue","name":"祖拜尔","text":"米奥，请为我确认，她是否合格。","id":341,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/7/72/Avg_avg_npc_1479_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1482_1#1$1","id":342},{"type":"dialogue","name":"米奥","text":"好的，祖拜尔，如果那是你的愿望。","id":343,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/d5/Avg_avg_npc_1482_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"米奥","text":"我会去的。","id":344,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/d5/Avg_avg_npc_1482_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":345},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":346},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":347},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"2","id":348},{"type":"charslot","id":349},{"type":"background","id":350},{"type":"image","id":351}],"characters":["？？？","佩佩","梅捷缇克缇","电台广播","祖拜尔","拉恕尔","米奥","沃奥"]}